，2024 年 1 季度的登记数量减少，表明疫情后的补偿效应已逐渐消退，且长期影响「婚姻市场」的因素依然在发挥作用。 何亚福说，尽管 2024 年出生人口可能会因延迟生育等因素有所回升，但从长期看，受年轻人口减少、生育观念变化等影响，中国生育率和出生人口数的下降趋势难以根本改变，除非未来实施强有力的生育支持政策以应对这一挑战。2024 年 1 季度结婚登记同比减少 17.8 万对"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-41417b700252fa51ff82239e22da1677_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/659303634"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI78Tb/Ni69o1KEAMaCTEwODc4OTcyMSDTv8izBjAAOIEDQB1yCTY1OTMwMzYzNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1718803319.177697", "card_id": "Q_656999873", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《星穹铁道》持明族，如果只有「白露」可以生孩子会怎样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8ae484cd3abe6a8cc57066afb81bf4d6_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656999873"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I78Tb/Ni69o1KEAMaCTEwODI3NzgzNyDExb+yBjAAOCdAHnIJNjU2OTk5ODczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1718803319.177899", "card_id": "Q_658202339", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 236}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "AI 时代，高考选什么专业比较有前景？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b09dff85db79dd476c96d5992aac12ab_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658202339"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI78Tb/Ni69o1KEAMaCT